Author: fishonthesun
Text: Wow a lot of this rings true for me. Except we never had pop, just milk. My dad was totally addicted to mt dew and when he stopped drinking it he lost 40 pounds in like 6 months. Now he drinks Pepsi and complains about getting fat lol. I try to point out to him (in a kind way) when he is adding extra calories he doesnt need cause he is genuinely trying to lose weight but is getting frustrated. He blamed it on a lack of testosterone that comes with aging, lol.  I blame it on his relationship with his girlfriend, they love to cook food together but then they eat too much  Anyways, gotta love em
